	| v1.0 | 2025-06-17 | cyanezf | First version |
	
	# Dependencies
	| Dependency |
	|:-----------|
	  
	# Description
	This function checks the `year` and returns whether it is a leap year or not.
	
	## Return
	| bool | description |
	|:---:|:------------|
	| 0 | It's not a leap year |
	| 1 | It's a leap year |
	
	#
